trans-unit.source: Manages the overflow behavior of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Administrerer overflyt virkemåten for en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If there are more overflow items than can be displayed on the form, use the [ToolStrip Items Collection Editor](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e681f3ab-94ba-4b2b-ac64-1dfad46caa25) to manage this situation.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes flere overflyt-elementer enn det som kan vises i skjemaet, kan du bruke den [ToolStrip elementer samlingen redigeringsprogrammet](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e681f3ab-94ba-4b2b-ac64-1dfad46caa25) til å administrere denne situasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflow"></xref> class derived from a base <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflow"> </xref> klasse avledet fra en base <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem"></xref> from which to derive this <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflow"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem"> </xref> som avledes dette <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflow"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new accessibility object for the control.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter et nytt tilgjengelighet-objekt for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: If you do not explicitly call the CreateAccessibilityInstance method, it will be called when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.AccessibilityObject%2A> property is referenced.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke eksplisitt kalle metoden CreateAccessibilityInstance, den kan kalles når den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.AccessibilityObject%2A>egenskapen det refereres til.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.AccessibilityObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > To get or set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.AccessibilityObject%2A> property, you must add a reference to the `Accessibility` assembly installed with the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Ikke hente eller angi den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.AccessibilityObject%2A>-egenskapen, må du legge til en referanse til det `Accessibility` samlingen er installert med den [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.AccessibilityObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: A new <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.AccessibleObject"></xref> for the control.
trans-unit.target: En ny <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.AccessibleObject"> </xref> for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Gets all of the items that are currently being displayed on the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter alle elementene som vises for øyeblikket på den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Use the DisplayedItems property to get everything the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> currently displays, including items the user did not add, such as a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflowButton>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk DisplayedItems-egenskapen for å hente alt <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>for øyeblikket vises, inkludert elementer brukeren ikke legge til, for eksempel <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflowButton>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflowButton> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflow.Items%2A> property to get all items on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>, including those not being displayed.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflow.Items%2A>til å hente alle elementer den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>, inkludert de som ikke vises.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflow.Items%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemCollection"></xref> that includes all items on this <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemCollection"> </xref> som inkluderer alle elementer i denne <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the size of a rectangular area into which a control can be fitted.
trans-unit.target: Henter størrelsen på et rektangulært område som en kontroll kan tilpasses.

trans-unit.source: The custom-sized area for a control.
trans-unit.target: Egendefinert størrelse området for en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: An ordered pair of type <xref href="System.Drawing.Size"></xref> representing the width and height of a rectangle.
trans-unit.target: En i par med typen <xref href="System.Drawing.Size"> </xref> som representerer bredden og høyden på et rektangel.

trans-unit.source: Gets all of the items on the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref>, whether they are currently being displayed or not.
trans-unit.target: Henter alle elementene den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"> </xref>, om de for øyeblikket vises eller ikke.

trans-unit.source: Use the Items property to get all items on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>, including those not being displayed.
trans-unit.target: Bruke egenskapen elementer ikke hente alle elementer i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>, inkludert de som ikke vises.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflow.DisplayedItems%2A> property to get only those items that are currently displayed on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflow.DisplayedItems%2A>til å hente elementene som vises for øyeblikket på <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripOverflow.DisplayedItems%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemCollection"></xref> containing all of the items.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemCollection"> </xref> som inneholder alle elementene.

trans-unit.source: Passes a reference to the cached <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.LayoutEngine*> returned by the layout engine interface.
trans-unit.target: Sender en referanse til den bufrede <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.LayoutEngine*>returnert av motoren grensesnittet oppsettet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.LayoutEngine*>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Layout.LayoutEngine"></xref> that represents the cached layout engine returned by the layout engine interface.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Layout.LayoutEngine"> </xref> som representerer bufrede oppsettet-motor ble returnert av grensesnittet for oppsett av motoren.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.Layout"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Hever den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.Layout"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: Raising an event invokes the event handler through a delegate.
trans-unit.target: Opprettet en hendelse aktiverer hendelsesbehandlingen via en representant.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Events](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [hendelser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The OnLayout method also allows derived classes to handle the event without attaching a delegate.
trans-unit.target: Metoden OnLayout kan også avledede klasser behandle hendelsen uten å knytte representant.

trans-unit.source: This is the preferred technique for handling the event in a derived class.
trans-unit.target: Dette er den foretrukne metoden for behandling av hendelsen i en avledet klasse.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LayoutEventArgs"></xref> that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LayoutEventArgs"> </xref> som inneholder Hendelsesdata.

trans-unit.source: Resets the collection of displayed and overflow items after a layout is done.
trans-unit.target: Tilbakestiller samlingen av vises overflyt og elementer når en oppsettet er ferdig.
